# OurToken (OT)

OurToken is an ERC20 token implementation using OpenZeppelin's ERC20 contract. This token is created as part of a Foundry project and includes basic functionalities such as transfers, allowances, and minting during deployment.

## Features

- ERC20-compliant token.
- Token name: **Our Token**
- Token symbol: **OT**
- Initial supply minted to the deployer's address during deployment.

## Prerequisites

To work with this project, ensure you have the following installed:

- [Foundry](https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry) (An Ethereum development environment)
- [Node.js and npm](https://nodejs.org/) (optional, for additional tooling)
